Finally, you''ll hear about what you can do to #BanThisBS.(biometric surveillance). In January 2021, we''re preparing a week of action and if you''re ready & willing - you have a role in it. More, in 2021 we aim to gather over 1 million signatures part of a special petition - European Citizen Initiative (ECI). The ECI forces the European Commission to formally respond to us and address our call for a BAN. You''ll hear a bit also about how you can help reach those 1 million signatures.','2000-02-02 00:00:00');

