INSERT INTO "T_Extended_Description" VALUES(246,1468322310,'We metabolize, we digest, we compose and decompose. Together with DIY approach we will destille and introduce into the art of destillilling and create odore and sounds of nature. We create steam, extract essences, smell the scent and float it into space. Nature has all properties of self healing and remedy. We use spells and magic for coevolution within cyberspace. Nature fights back is a sound composition by Princessin in Not in collaboration with BadLab Project.','2000-02-02 00:00:00');
